Title: Bioequivalence Study Bevacizumab Biosimilar (BEVZ92) Versus Bevacizumab (AVASTIN®) in First-line Treatment mCRC Patients
Conditions: Metastatic Colorectal Cancer (mCRC)
Phase: PHASE1
Status: COMPLETED
Primary outcomes: Area Under the Concentration-versus-time Curve (AUC) at Cycle 1 (AUC0-336h) of BEVZ92 and Avastin®; AUC at Steady State (AUCss) of BEVZ92 and Avastin®